name: DIEGO - "EL GOL DEL SIGLO" (The goal of the century)
description:
At 55 minutes of the match, Maradona dribbled around 60 meters and left behind 5 english players including the goalkeeper and scored. "The goal of the century" was the second goal of Diego Armando Maradona to England in the FIFA World cup of 86.  The final results of the match was England 1 - 2 Argentina. Then Argentina raised the cup against Germany.

Intervened photography
